{
  "stem": "1917.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 382.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After registration and tattooing, our clothes were returned to us with a huge oil paint, red cross, painted on the back from shoulder to shoulder from the top of the neck all the way to the bottom of the dress.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, why on earth would they ruin our nice dresses with the red paint?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I took a Holocaust 101 class in 1979, I asked my professor maybe he could help me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, well, you were part of medical experiments.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What did you expect to have on your back?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, we were marched between the barbed wire out from that camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was evening already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Women prisoners were returning from work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These were not women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were walking human skeletons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One poor woman saw us and started yelling, children, children, where did you come from?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hoping, of course, to find something about her own child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She never found out, because the SS ordered the two huge German shepherds, and they tore her to pieces in front of us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That picture, unfortunately, was repeated many times during our stay in Auschwitz, because anytime we walked, we always walked under SS supervision.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people would see us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They always wanted to find out who we were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We entered the barrack in Camp A in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And two twins-- I think that they were probably 11 or 12, Hungarians, called Judith and Lea.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They showed us to our bunk beds, which were a skinny, little bunk bed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We slept in it about four children on occasion when it was very full, at best, two.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we hardly came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
